				<div class="content">
										<div class="post-title">
						<h2><a href="http://www.webtoolkit.info/javascript-custom-cursor.html" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Javascript custom cursor">Javascript custom cursor</a></h2>
					</div>
					<!--/post-title -->
					
          <p>This script will add a fancy custom crosshair mouse cursor to your website. You can modify this custom mouse cursor script anyway you want to add functionality and special effects. <span id="more-263"></span>You can even change the shape and color of the mouse cursor by changing the image (skin) file.</p>
<h2>Skins</h2>
<p><img style="border: 1px dashed silver; margin-right: 10px;" src="/djs/skin.gif" alt="custom javascript cursor" /> <img style="border: 1px dashed silver; margin-right: 10px;" src="/djs/skin1.gif" alt="custom javascript cursor" /></p>
<h2><a href="/demo/javascript-custom-cursor" title="Demo - Javascript custom cursor"><strong>DEMO</strong></a></h2>
<h3><strong>Source code for index.html</strong></h3>

